  <brief_title>Assessment Of Vascular Health After Niacin Therapy (AVANT)</brief_title>
  <acronym>AVANT</acronym>
  <official_title>A 12-WEEK STUDY EVALUATING THE EFFECTS OF NIACIN ON VASCULAR HEALTH ASSESSED BY FLUORODEOXYGLUCOSE-PET/CT AND CIRCULATING ENDOTHELIAL PROGENITOR CELLS AND MICROPARTICLES</official_title>
