  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is looking to see if niacin will lessen atherosclerotic plaque inflammation and
      favorably affect circulating levels of endothelial progenitor cells and microparticles in
      people with atherosclerotic disease on chronic statin therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
